{"tid":1538672,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"堅持叫五大訴求係要話人聽，我地始終如一，冇變過質，唔比位人上綱上線","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:41:22.000Z","uid":63846,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"3435328c4cfb33a1fd67f41d4211faef23412aff","tid":1538672,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:02.000Z","msg":"五大訴求，缺一不可<br />\n<br />\n你話好唔好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"151dd3c555dab31221ca063f85fb5f6f79d18f58","tid":1538672,"uid":23046,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:32.000Z","msg":"撤你老母咩，條柒頭撤再講<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538583\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538583</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n真正港人唔會唔知咩事，點都會繼續出<br />\n唔好再開po講喇，人地都未講撤<br />\n我地就自亂陣腳<br />\n推番行動po啦<br />\n唔好洗走有用資訊<br />\n唔好出冇用既po<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"416381fe84d750cda1635881c259ca975b01f971","tid":1538672,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:37.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f29788cbab3d2a905936490229a62521dd0894e","tid":1538672,"uid":287594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:34:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QUGSMa3.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQUGSMa3.gif&h=1c74332a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【長期抗爭】最簡單有效嘅日常抗爭<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538155\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538155</a>"},{"pid":"dd4470bc8af9fa14ca612f2367ec12803b885dae","tid":1538672,"uid":63846,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:41:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}